Original work by Soqucoin: the Dilithium key-management layer (`CDilithiumKey`,
PAT type aliases, and a `randombytes` shim that delegates to Bitcoin Core's
`GetStrongRandBytes`). Licensed under the MIT License; the full license text is
in the repository root `COPYING`.

NOTE: the `dilithium-ref/` subdirectory vendors the PQ-Crystals CRYSTALS-Dilithium
reference implementation under its own upstream license — see
`src/pat/dilithium-ref/LICENSE`. The files directly in this directory
(`keys.*`, `types.h`, `randombytes.cpp`) are original Soqucoin work and are not
derived from third-party source code.
